    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you looking for a ride that\u2019s practically brand new? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it\u2019s in flawless condition\u2014inside and out! It\u2019s been pampered since day one and looks like it just rolled off the showroom floor. No scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy this beauty! Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
