      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage. The exterior is flawless, featuring original factory paint with a deep, mirror-like luster, free of rock chips, swirls, or imperfections. Every body panel aligns perfectly, reflecting its accident-free history. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the leather upholstery remains supple with no bolster wear, and the original carpets have been protected by premium mats since day one. All electronic systems, from the infotainment to the ambient lighting, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car is turn-key. It comes with a complete, documented service history, including recent fluid services and a brand-new set of high-performance tires. This is a rare opportunity to own a preserved example of automotive excellence. We welcome independent inspections to confirm its pristine status.",
